'''Mike Richardson''' is the founder and CEO of [[Dark Horse Comics]].<ref name="DH History">{{DarkHorse|url=Company/History|text=History}}</ref> A comics author, Richardson co-wrote ''[[Star Wars: Crimson Empire]]'', ''[[Crimson Empire II: Council of Blood]]'', and ''[[Star Wars: Crimson Empire III&mdash;Empire Lost]]'' with [[Randy Stradley]].

